title: Ramayanam Malayalam Katharoopathil [svprasad]
description:
Ramayana Tathvam is the essence and philosophy of the epic Ramayanam, recorded on 


soundtrack. This compact set of 2 audio CDs in MP3 format covers the entire 



Ramayanam and contains musical rendition of selected verses.


From school of Bhagavad Gita

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Poornamaya Ramayana katha ningalkku pramukharude sabdathil (prof Aliyar ,Bhagya 


Lekshmi) malayalatthil aswadikkam ...ellavarum seed chyuka
